  orderNo 49
  title [Omitted.].
  content `Power of Chairperson to transfer cases. [Omitted by s.11, ibid. (w.e.f. 24-8-2010)].`
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_42_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_19_22_00003_200152_1517807324452&sectionId=24784&sectionno=42&orderno=49&orgactid=AC_CEN_19_22_00003_200152_1517807324452
obj_root_law_sections_42_footnotes:
